reviewText:
Editorial Reviews

Willy Fog, eccentric British millionaire and lion, and his animal friends embark on a dangerous mission to the Earth's core in this animated program, inspired by the classic book by Jules Verne. Willy, Romy, Rigadon and Tico set out a thrilling journey into the unknown as they make their way to the center of the Earth. Along the way, the group must overcome a series of dangerous obstacles as they make their way through endless passages and subterranean caves.
